'S e [[prìomh-bhaile]] [[Leabanon]] a tha ann an 
'''Beirut''', ([[Arabais]]: '''بيروت''' , Bayrūt, [[Greugais]]: '''Βηρυττός''').   Mar is trice bidh  muinntir na dùthcha a' cleachdadh an ainm [[Fraingis]]: '''Beyrouth'''.
'S e am baile as motha na dùthcha cuideachd. 

Tha Beirut suidhichte eadar a' bheinn ''Mount Lebanon''  agus cladach [[Mediterranean Sea| a’ Mhuir Mheadanach]]. Tha [[Tripolis]] agus [[Byblos]]  san tuath aige agus tha [[Sidon]] agus [[Tyre]] sa deas aige.

Tha mòran ionaidean eadar-nàiseanta  ann am Beirut:
m.e.:
* [[na Dùthchannan Aonaichte]] 
* Economic and Social Commission for Western Asia(ESCWA) <ref>[http://www.unfpa.org/icpd5/bulletins/bulletn4.htm ICPD+5 NEWS BULLETIN], United Nations General Assembly, 2007</ref><ref>[http://www.escwa.org.lb/ United Nations Economic and Social Commission for Western Asia]</ref> 

* International Labour Organization (ILO)<ref>[http://www.ilo.org.lb/ International Labour Organization (Lebanon)]</ref> 
*  [[UNESCO]] oifis airson na dùthchanan Araibianach <ref>[http://portal.unesco.org/beirut UNESCO Beirut]</ref> 

Tha port-adhar eadar-nàiseanta aige, am ''Beirut Rafic Hariri International Airport'', suidhichte deas air a’ bhaile. 
<ref>[http://www.beirutairport.gov.lb/historical.html History] Beirut Rafic Hariri, Port-adhar eadar-nàiseanta</ref>

